enchantment.ne.neko_blade.desc: The lower the durability of the weapon the higher the damage increase, up to 1.15x.
enchantment.ne.neko_god.desc: Very low probability of dealing command level damage, probability affected by luck.
enchantment.ne.neko_meow.desc: The attack itself makes a catcall. Nothing more.
enchantment.ne.neko_king.desc: You can use minerals to strengthen your weapon, adding 1 point of damage for every 20 points of strengthening.
enchantment.ne.neko_emperor.desc: The number of kills will be recorded, and for every 50 kills, 1 point of damage will be added.
enchantment.ne.neko_day.desc: Increases damage during the day and decreases it at night.
enchantment.ne.neko_night.desc: Increases damage at night and decreases it during the day.
enchantment.ne.neko_ninja.desc: Goes into stealth when taking damage and increases damage.
enchantment.ne.neko_soul.desc: Gain souls per attack, and spend 200 souls to heal 10% of your life when wounded.
enchantment.ne.neko_blessing.desc: Gain one tier of blessing per cat bred, reducing by two tiers when the cat dies. Consume one tier of blessing to reduce damage when injured, stackable.
enchantment.ne.neko_mirror.desc: Has a chance to bounce back damage when injured and is immune to this damage.
enchantment.ne.neko_life.desc: Has a probability to mitigate damage greater than 20% of life and less than 150% to 20%.
enchantment.ne.neko_chop.desc: There is a probability of obtaining a biological head
enchantment.ne.z_confusion.desc: Attacked creatures treat other creatures nearest to the player as targets
enchantment.ne.zi_bright.desc: Monsters avoid it when holding it.
enchantment.ne.zi_alone.desc: Only this enchantment provides a damage bonus that varies with the number of times it is used.
enchantment.ne.zi_indestructible.desc: Prevent destruction when in a dropped state.
enchantment.ne.zi_unbreakable.desc: Use NETHERITE BLOCK at the Anvil to strengthen it five times to unlock it.
enchantment.ne.curse_disease.desc: Gain random negative effects when attacking
enchantment.ne.corrode.desc: Attacks have a chance to lose half of their current durability
